column2: VVVVVV. Floor plan doubles through effortless gravity switching! Ceiling adhesive furniture included.
Celeste. Need chore assistance? Summon an evil clone to duplicate your actions!
Pong provides unmatchable security benefits: our AI paddles direct balls toward intruders!
Sims. “Feed into your shut-in lifestyle; grocery shop straight from the refrigerator!”
Plants vs Zombies. Sentient plants water themselves, giving you a self-watering garden!
Animal Crossing. Tight budgets become resolved now that money grows on trees!
Experienced two major tragedies? Feeling fearful? Choose Half-Life: the third won't come...
“Animal Crossing is eternal paradise! Expect multiple eternal paradises if you’re popular…”
